            <h3 class="comment-title" data-subject="Re:Truth is the best defence"><i class="com-toggle fa fa-caret-down"></i>Re:Truth is the best defence<span> (1, Insightful)</span></h3>
            <h4 class="avatar-tiny"><a href="//beta.slashdot.org/~fuzzyfuzzyfungus" class="author" title="author name and user ID">fuzzyfuzzyfungus (1223518) </a> | about a year ago | <a href="//beta.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=3669841&cid=43505661">(#43505661)</a></h4>
