            <h4 class="avatar-tiny"><a href="//beta.slashdot.org/~Hentes" class="author" title="author name and user ID">Hentes (2461350) </a> | about a year ago | <a href="//beta.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=3669841&cid=43505571">(#43505571)</a></h4>
