        <header data-points="1" data-reason="Normal">
            <h3 class="comment-title" data-subject="Re:Am I the only one......"><i class="com-toggle fa fa-caret-down"></i>Re:Am I the only one......<span> (1)</span></h3>
            <h4 class="avatar-tiny"><a href="//beta.slashdot.org/~firex726" class="author" title="author name and user ID">firex726 (1188453) </a> | about a year ago | <a href="//beta.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=3669841&cid=43505655">(#43505655)</a></h4>
        </header>
        <div id="comment_body_43505655" class="comment-wrapper" data-points="1" data-reason="Normal">
            <div class="comment-body"><p>Technically this is libel; but slander too can damage one's reputation.</p></div>
            <footer class="comment-footer" id="comment_footer_43505655">
